<h3 id="programming-languages-and-it">Programming Languages and IT</h3>

<p>I’m interested in programming languages and related technologies as they pertain to
software and systems development, e.g. Haskell ecosystem, Nix and NixOS, (Doom) Emacs and
modal editing (in the spirit of <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vi</code>), Linux and Open Source Software, verified software
and interactive theorem provers (especially, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Coq</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Agda</code>). Check out:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/ghc/ghc/search?o=desc&amp;q=author%3Aulysses4ever&amp;s=committer-date&amp;type=Commits">My contributions to the GHC Haskell compiler</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.tweag.io/blog/2019-09-25-bazel-ghc-persistent-worker-internship/">Blog post about my internship at Tweag I/O in 2019</a></li>
</ul>





